<div class="timeline">
  <div class="timeline-item">
    <span class="timeline-date">~2022</span>
    <div class="timeline-card">
      <h3 data-cms-field="weg_1_h3">The Beginning</h3>
      <p data-cms-field="weg_1_p">Gym. First fitness routine. The body becomes a project.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="timeline-item">
    <span class="timeline-date">2023</span>
    <div class="timeline-card">
      <h3 data-cms-field="weg_2_h3">Getting Serious</h3>
      <p data-cms-field="weg_2_p">Training gets serious. The body becomes priority. The switch flips.</p>
      <p class="timeline-quote" data-cms-field="weg_2_quote">"CONSISTENCY AND TRUST guide me."</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="timeline-item">
    <span class="timeline-date">Sep 2024</span>
    <div class="timeline-card">
      <h3 data-cms-field="weg_3_h3">First Triathlon</h3>
      <p data-cms-field="weg_3_p">Hannover Volkstriathlon — sprint distance. 12th in age group. 1:24:10.</p>
      <p class="timeline-quote" data-cms-field="weg_3_quote">"It was insanely fantastic, it was a milestone! I want more."</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="timeline-item">
    <span class="timeline-date">May 2025</span>
    <div class="timeline-card">
      <h3 data-cms-field="weg_4_h3">5150 IM Kraichgau</h3>
      <p data-cms-field="weg_4_p">First Olympic triathlon. 6th in age group. 2:52:57.</p>
      <p class="timeline-quote" data-cms-field="weg_4_quote">"I always cry at the finish line, it's so much hard work put into it, I get deeply emotional and proud of myself. VAMOOOOO!"</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="timeline-item">
    <span class="timeline-date">Jul 2025</span>
    <div class="timeline-card">
      <h3 data-cms-field="weg_5_h3">WTCS Hamburg</h3>
      <p data-cms-field="weg_5_p">Short distance. 7th in age group. 2:36:49.</p>
      <p class="timeline-quote" data-cms-field="weg_5_quote">"My jump at the finish line replaces all possible captions — WHAT A DAY! UNSTOPPABLE."</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="timeline-item">
    <span class="timeline-date">Sep 2025</span>
    <div class="timeline-card">
      <h3 data-cms-field="weg_6_h3">70.3 IM Emilia Romagna</h3>
      <p data-cms-field="weg_6_p">Cervia. 9th in age group. 5:42:36.</p>
      <p class="timeline-quote" data-cms-field="weg_6_quote">"35°C on my head, dehydration already at km 50 on the bike, with a headache and sickness that somehow brought me to the finish line."</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="timeline-item timeline-highlight">
    <span class="timeline-date">Apr 2026</span>
    <div class="timeline-card">
      <h3 data-cms-field="weg_7_h3">Qualification Brasília</h3>
      <p data-cms-field="weg_7_p">The ticket to Nice. Everything leads here.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="timeline-item timeline-highlight">
    <span class="timeline-date">2026</span>
    <div class="timeline-card">
      <h3 data-cms-field="weg_8_h3">Ironman World Championship Nice</h3>
      <p data-cms-field="weg_8_p">The goal. The world championship. Amateur — for now.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
